article.description: — Kevon Voyles had 18 points in Marshall's 80-69 victory over Florida International at the Cayman Islands Classic on Monday night.
article.headline: Voyles leads Marshall over Florida International 80-69 at Cayman Islands Classic
article.linkText: Voyles leads Marshall over Florida International 80-69 at Cayman Islands Classic
article.story: GEORGE TOWN, Cayman Islands -- — Kevon Voyles had 18 points in Marshall's 80-69 victory over Florida International at the Cayman Islands Classic on Monday night. Voyles added three steals for the Thundering Herd (2-2). Wyatt Fricks scored 15 points while going 6 of 8 from the field. Jacob Conner had 15 points and shot 6 for 9, including 3 for 5 from beyond the arc. Jonathan Aybar led the way for the Panthers (1-5) with 13 points and two steals. Petar Krivokapic added 12 points and four steals for Florida International. Arturo Dean also had 11 points, six rebounds, four assists and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
